Use this operation to delete a human task user interface (worker task template)

Source: R/sagemaker_operations.R
sagemaker_delete_human_task_ui.Rd

Use this operation to delete a human task user interface (worker task template).

To see a list of human task user interfaces (work task templates) in your account, use . When you delete a worker task template, it no longer appears when you call list_human_task_uis.

sagemaker_delete_human_task_ui(HumanTaskUiName)

Arguments

HumanTaskUiName

[required] The name of the human task user interface (work task template) you want to delete.

Value

An empty list.

Request syntax

svc$delete_human_task_ui(
  HumanTaskUiName = "string"
)
